<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="offend-v">offend <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'fend/    美 /ə'fend/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>得罪；冒犯；令人不适：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please follow your project supervisor’s instructions, or you’ll offend him.
要听从你项目主管的指示，否则你会使他生气。</p></div></div>